KG name: Copac: union catalogue of major University- Specialist- and National Libraries in the UK and Ireland
Description: The Copac National Academic & Specialist Library catalogue. Copac gives free access to the merged catalogues of an increasing diversity of libraries within the UK and Ireland with a focus on those of particular importance to researchers. These range from small specialist libraries- such as the National Trust and Royal Botanic Gardens Kew- through major universities- such as Oxford University- to the UK National Libraries including the British Library catalogues.Data is available in XML via a range of machine-to-machine interfaces. More information about the interfaces is available at:[http://copac.ac.uk/interfaces/](http://copac.ac.uk/interfaces/)A small sample of linked data is also available:[http://data.copac.ac.uk/](http://data.copac.ac.uk/)
